CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 25, 2014

[Cite as 03/25/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-1170.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2014-0415. In re K.D.

Franklin App. Nos. 13AP-607 and 13AP-667, 2014-Ohio-278. This cause is pending before the court as a jurisdictional appeal. Upon review of the appeal, it appears that the case involves the termination of parental rights.

Accordingly, it is ordered by the court, sua sponte, that this case shall proceed according to the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio that pertain to cases involving the termination of parental rights. Appellee’s memorandum in response shall be filed no later than 15 days from the date of this entry.
